  &lt;img data-src=&#34;https://hughandbecky.us/Hugh-CV/Hugh-CV/post/olac-grant-aggregator/NSF-Grant_hue2c2cdacdb65db441481dd609fada4c1_318924_2000x2000_fit_q90_lanczos.jpg&#34; class=&#34;lazyload&#34; alt=&#34;Notice of NSF Grant award&#34; width=&#34;1436&#34; height=&#34;881&#34; itemprop=&#34;contentUrl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;
  
  &lt;figcaption&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Notice of NSF Grant award
      
&lt;span class=&#34;img-attribution&#34;&gt;Credit: &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/showAward.do?AwardNumber=0966411&amp;amp;WT.z_pims_id=12816&#34;&gt; NSF&lt;span itemprop=&#34;creator&#34; itemtype=&#34;https://schema.org/Person&#34; itemscope&gt;
        &lt;meta itemprop=&#34;name&#34; content=&#34;NSF&#34; /&gt;
      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I was particularly happy to find that NSF does have a &lt;em&gt;grant offering&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;grant awarded&lt;/em&gt; 
&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/progSearch.do?WT.si_n=ClickedAbstractsRecentAwards&amp;amp;WT.si_x=1&amp;amp;WT.si_cs=1&amp;amp;WT.z_pims_id=12816&amp;amp;SearchType=progSearch&amp;amp;page=2&amp;amp;QueryText=&amp;amp;ProgOrganization=&amp;amp;ProgOfficer=&amp;amp;ProgEleCode=7719&amp;amp;BooleanElement=true&amp;amp;ProgRefCode=&amp;amp;BooleanRef=true&amp;amp;ProgProgram=&amp;amp;ProgFoaCode=&amp;amp;RestrictActive=on&amp;amp;Search=Search#results&#34; title=&#34;NSF Grants&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;search section&lt;/a&gt;. But aggregating this knowledge with prior research would really give interested parties in particular languages the integrated perspective of how funding has impacted the development and research of minority languages.&lt;/p&gt;
